  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要梳理一下风险响应的工作流。当团队在KanbanBoard上发现风险时，应该先汇总到SprintBacklog里做统一评估，而不是直接分散处理。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Groupware_KanbanBoard",
        "Groupware_SprintBacklog"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "明白，所以起点是KanbanBoard，然后流向SprintBacklog做聚合。那评估之后怎么分流呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Groupware_KanbanBoard",
        "Groupware_SprintBacklog"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "评估后按优先级走三条路径：高风险直接回到KanbanBoard立即处理；中高风险的走WikiPage沉淀方案；中低风险的进ChatRoom快速同步就行。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Groupware_SprintBacklog",
        "Groupware_KanbanBoard",
        "Groupware_WikiPage",
        "Groupware_ChatRoom"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我在SprintBacklog后面加了判断节点，分出三条带标签的线：高、中高、中低，分别连到KanbanBoard、WikiPage和ChatRoom。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Groupware_SprintBacklog",
        "Groupware_KanbanBoard",
        "Groupware_WikiPage",
        "Groupware_ChatRoom"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，高风险那条线——我的意思是\"高优先级风险\"需要立即行动，所以回到KanbanBoard进入执行态，但这里容易和起点的KanbanBoard混淆，需要区分清楚。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Groupware_KanbanBoard"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "了解，虽然都是KanbanBoard，但逻辑上是两个阶段：起点是\"发现风险\"，返回是\"执行应对\"。我在图里用流程顺序来体现这个区别。那这三条路径最后怎么汇合？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Groupware_KanbanBoard",
        "Groupware_WikiPage",
        "Groupware_ChatRoom"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "无论哪条路径，最终都要录入IssueTracker做跟踪闭环。KanbanBoard的高风险项、WikiPage的方案、ChatRoom的同步记录，都需要沉淀为可追踪的issue。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Groupware_KanbanBoard",
        "Groupware_WikiPage",
        "Groupware_ChatRoom",
        "Groupware_IssueTracker"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加：从KanbanBoard、WikiPage、ChatRoom三条线都指向IssueTracker。看起来是个菱形汇聚结构。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Groupware_KanbanBoard",
        "Groupware_WikiPage",
        "Groupware_ChatRoom",
        "Groupware_IssueTracker"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "IssueTracker之后还需要一步——已解决的issue要回到KanbanBoard的Done列或者归档区，完成整个循环。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Groupware_IssueTracker",
        "Groupware_KanbanBoard"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "加上了，IssueTracker指向最后的KanbanBoard，形成闭环。我检查下整体结构：发现→评估→分流处理→跟踪→归档，五步完整。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Groupware_IssueTracker",
