      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "不对，我刚才看错了——SprintBacklog到KanbanBoard那条线，标签我写的是\"高\"，但应该是单向的响应流程，不是双向循环。让我再确认下流向。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Groupware_SprintBacklog",
        "Groupware_KanbanBoard"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下：SprintBacklog→KanbanBoard是\"高\"风险的处理路径，IssueTracker→KanbanBoard是闭环归档，这两个KanbanBoard节点虽然同名但时序不同，没有双向循环问题。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Groupware_SprintBacklog",
        "Groupware_KanbanBoard",
        "Groupware_IssueTracker"
